### Web Forms Kya Hain? (Simple Definition)
Web forms users se data collect karne aur UI control karne ka powerful tool hain (jaise login, signup, feedback, shopping cart).  
Yeh **HTML + CSS + JavaScript** ka perfect combination maangte hain kyunki forms complex hote hain.

**Prerequisites (Pehle yeh seekh lo):**
- Introduction to HTML (complete)
- Basic native form controls
- CSS aur JavaScript ka basic knowledge

### Recommended Learning Path (Introductory Tutorials)

| Order | Tutorial Title                          | Asan Description                                                                 | Kya Seekhoge? |
|-------|-----------------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------|---------------|
| 1     | **Your first form**                     | Pehli baar simple form banayein – HTML structure, basic styling aur data server pe bhejna | Form basics, `<form>`, `<input>`, `<label>`, `<button>`, simple CSS, form submission |
| 2     | **How to structure a web form**         | Form ko semantically aur achhe se structure karna (meaningful markup)            | `<fieldset>`, `<legend>`, `<label>`, proper grouping, accessibility |

**Tip:** Pehle "Your first form" se shuru karo, phir structure wala tutorial padho. Iske baad hi advanced parts (controls, styling, validation) samajh aayenge.

